node.text:
July 21, 2021– JALISCO, Mexico - 
BLUE AGAVE ORIGIN has been a project which has been a collaboration between the Mexican Space Agency (Agencia Espacial Mexicana) and JAJA Spirits which began in 2019.

At 9:45AM CST this morning, the first Tequila bottle using 100% Agave Azul has crossed into space. Representatives from JAJA celebrated on the ground by consuming shots of JAJA Blanco which was the variant of JAJA Tequila chosen for the adventurous mission.

This morning’s trip to space comes amid a month of significant new milestones in space tourism, as Virgin CEO Richard Branson, and former Amazon CEO Jeff Bezos have both achieved what JAJA has today. 

#blueorigin #jeffbezos
